# TEMP IGNORES FOR CAMERONCROW (local-only: reference packs, scratch, notes)
planning/
CLAUDE.md

# graphify: track the graph itself (graph.json, manifest.json, GRAPH_REPORT.md,
# graph.html, cost.json) so it persists across machines; ignore regenerable
# cache + machine-local hook/interpreter state (canonical block - see
# git-hooks/README.md; the post-commit hook keeps this in sync everywhere)
graphify-out/cache/
graphify-out/.graphify_detect.err
graphify-out/.graphify_python
graphify-out/.graphify_root
graphify-out/.commits_since_update
graphify-out/.needs_update
graphify-out/.hook_update.log
graphify-out/20*/
# reference shaderpacks kept on disk for re-anchoring, never committed
Eclipse-Shader-Unstable/
Bliss_v2.1.2_(Chocapic13_Shaders_edit)/
# .irlights patch recipes ship in the consumer mods, not in core
*.irlights
